snippet.title: Fleetcom Launch Trailer | Halo Infinite
snippet.description:
Operation: Fleetcom heats up Halo Infinite with classic modes and new challenges! VIP from Halo 3 returns—protect your VIP and score points. Headhunter from Halo: Reach is coming soon—collect and deposit skulls to win.  

Grab the free Operation Pass for the iconic Operator armor or upgrade to Premium for the Reach Commando weapon model and Crimson Snowfall coating! 

Read more here:  http://aka.ms/FleetcomOperationLaunch

#halo #haloinfinite #halofleetcom
